KINFRA Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 04 Project Management Executive Posts
Harshitha / All Government Jobs / Aug 07, 2025, 10:11 IST
 Centre for Management Development, Kerala
 4 Jobs |  Posted On : 07-Aug-2025 |  Kerala |  Salary : 30,000 to 30,000




FOLLOW

The Kerala Industrial Infrastructure Development Corporation (KINFRA) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 04 Project Management Executive Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their B.E./B. Tech in Civil Engineering, MBA can apply for the KINFRA Recruitment 2025. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application fee, salary, and how to apply for these posts before the deadline. The application dates have already begun.




If you are more interested in Government Jobs, candidates can also apply for jobs in Kerala.

KINFRA Recruitment 2025 Eligibility Criteria:
Name of the Posts	Vacancies	Education
Project Management Executive	04	B.E./B. Tech in Civil Engineering, MBA

KINFRA Recruitment 2025 Age Limit:

The minimum age limit: 21 years.
The maximum age limit: 30 Years.
Age relaxation is based on the Organisation's norms.

KINFRA Recruitment 2025 Selection Process:

The selection process includes

Written Test.
Group Discussion.
Skill Test.
Interview.

KINFRA Recruitment 2025 Application Fee:

There is no application fee.

KINFRA Recruitment 2025 Pay Scale:

The basic pay: Rs. 30,000/- per month.
How to Apply for the KINFRA Recruitment 2025:
Go to the official website.
Visit the KINFRA Recruitment 2025 notification.
Read the instructions carefully and check the eligibility criteria.
Fill out the application form without any mistakes.
Pay the application fee (if needed).
Attach the required documents to the filled application form.
Submit the filled application form before the last date.
Download & take a printout of the filled application form for further use.

Important Dates:

Starting date	06-08-2025
Closing date	20-08-2025
